<section id="body">
	<video class="rightFloat" src="../Media/Unit04_e4a.flv" mode="16" id="1003"  /><video class="leftFloat" src="../Media/Unit04_e4b.flv" mode="16" id="1004"  /><video class="leftFloat" src="../Media/Unit04_e4c.flv" mode="16" id="1005"  /><video class="leftFloat" src="../Media/Unit04_e4d.flv" mode="16" id="1006"  /><br/><ol id="questionList"><br/><li id="1">How does Alexandra respond to this question?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q1" >She simply answers the question.</a></li><li><a id="q2" >She doesn't understand the question.</a></li><li><a id="q3" >She answers the question and adds more information.</a></li><li><a id="q4" >She answers the question and then talks about something else.</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="2">What does Alexandra say to this question?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q5" >She ignores the question and talks about something else.</a></li><li><a id="q6" >She answers the question.</a></li><li><a id="q7" >She seems to misunderstand the question.</a></li><li><a id="q8" >She needs help in understanding the question.</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="3">What does she do in response to this question?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q9" >She clarifies the question, gives her answer and says why.</a></li><li><a id="q10" >She misunderstands, so she talks about something else.</a></li><li><a id="q11" >She asks for clarification, disagrees and says why.</a></li><li><a id="q12" >She corrects the Examiner and then answers the question.</a></li></ol><br/></li><br/><li id="4">How does Alexandra respond to this question?<ol class="answerList"><li><a id="q13" >She says what she would have liked to do, but has not been able to.</a></li><li><a id="q14" >She doesn't answer the question properly.</a></li><li><a id="q15" >She lists things she would like to do in the future.</a></li><li><a id="q16" >She talks about her goals and what she has done so far to achieve them.</a></li></ol><br/></li></ol>
